The **NRGkick** {% term integration %} allows you to integrate your [NRGkick Gen2 mobile wallbox](https://www.nrgkick.com/en/) into Home Assistant. It uses the official local REST JSON API to communicate with the device.

## Prerequisites

To use this integration, your NRGkick device must meet the following requirements:

- **NRGkick Gen2** (Smart Cable)
- **Firmware**: SmartModule firmware 4.0.0.0 or newer
- **Local Network**: The device must be connected to the same local network as Home Assistant.
- **JSON API**: The JSON API must be enabled in the NRGkick App:
  1. Open the NRGkick app.
  2. Go to **Extended** > **Local API**.
  3. Enable **JSON API**.
  4. (Optional) Enable **Authentication (JSON)** and set a username and password.

